WEBVTT

01:37.100 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.479 --> 01:48.570
[Episode 8: Five-flavor fruit, sour, sweet, and warm, with an astringent property, good for qi boost, body fluid generation, kidney, and calming down.]

01:57.110 --> 01:57.870
Sir,

01:57.890 --> 01:58.560
time for business?

01:58.590 --> 01:59.560
Are you off work?

01:59.580 --> 02:00.210
Nice.

02:00.410 --> 02:01.130
Bye-bye.

02:15.310 --> 02:22.750
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

02:23.430 --> 02:31.110
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

02:31.680 --> 02:38.940
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

02:39.240 --> 02:46.010
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

02:46.110 --> 02:48.690
♫A gentle breeze begins to rise♫

02:50.680 --> 02:51.430
Shen Xifan

02:50.910 --> 02:55.460
♫You'll see a rainbow♫

02:55.480 --> 02:57.690
♫Hovering in mid-air♫

02:56.920 --> 02:57.970
Dr. Ho

02:58.800 --> 03:01.410
♫This sweet dream♫

03:03.410 --> 03:08.410
♫All our days are filled with♫

03:08.430 --> 03:12.020
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

03:09.000 --> 03:11.360
Do you usually commute by bus?

03:12.470 --> 03:20.360
♫Close your eyes, and love will never fade away♫

03:12.590 --> 03:14.080
This bus can

03:14.080 --> 03:16.000
take me right to the hotel shuttle stop.

03:16.000 --> 03:16.870
It's very convenient.

03:17.430 --> 03:18.280
Let's go have dinner.

03:18.280 --> 03:19.750
What would you like to eat? I'll order it.

03:22.740 --> 03:23.490
How about

03:24.050 --> 03:24.900
we go to my place...

03:28.300 --> 03:29.110
to make medicinal cuisine?

03:32.700 --> 03:34.490
I was just thinking about making it a couple of days ago.

03:34.520 --> 03:36.400
So I already bought all the herbs in advance.

03:36.420 --> 03:37.660
We can eat together.

03:40.140 --> 03:41.890
What? Is it not okay for you?

03:44.050 --> 03:44.770
Nope.

03:45.560 --> 03:46.430
It's okay.

03:47.000 --> 03:47.840
Let's go then.

03:48.570 --> 03:49.010
Come on.

03:51.950 --> 03:52.690
Let's go.

04:12.170 --> 04:13.560
Which floor do you live on?

04:14.380 --> 04:15.430
The 5th floor.

04:17.480 --> 04:18.410
I'm on the 12th.

04:19.290 --> 04:20.690
A higher floor.

04:21.360 --> 04:22.310
Higher is better.

04:22.330 --> 04:22.770
Yeah.

04:23.950 --> 04:24.560
Yes, it's quite good.

04:24.560 --> 04:25.630
Nice.

04:55.390 --> 04:56.270
Come in, please.

04:56.360 --> 04:56.990
Mm.

04:58.810 --> 05:00.200
I don't usually have visitors.

05:00.230 --> 05:02.020
So I only have disposable slippers.

05:03.420 --> 05:04.200
It's okay.

05:05.290 --> 05:06.240
I'll open a pair for you.

05:06.270 --> 05:06.910
Thank you.

05:09.910 --> 05:10.540
Change your shoes first.

05:10.560 --> 05:11.170
Okay.

05:13.720 --> 05:14.870
I'll go get you something to drink.

05:45.630 --> 05:46.630
The five-flavor fruit water.

05:47.570 --> 05:48.720
It replenishes qi and generates body fluids.

05:48.750 --> 05:49.750
You can give it a try.

05:49.770 --> 05:50.540
Thank you.

05:54.870 --> 05:55.480
It's so good.

05:55.800 --> 05:56.390
Right?

05:56.600 --> 05:57.560
Then drink some more.

06:00.270 --> 06:00.950
Don't just stand there.

06:00.950 --> 06:01.870
Go take a seat.

06:04.390 --> 06:05.750
It's a bit messy. Please don't mind it.

06:05.890 --> 06:06.840
It's okay.

06:07.430 --> 06:08.080
Sit down, please.

06:08.100 --> 06:09.210
I'm going to put some music on.

06:09.240 --> 06:09.870
Okay.

06:36.200 --> 06:43.730
♫So I wait and wander, but the outcome isn't so bad♫

06:36.420 --> 06:37.330
You can sit for a while.

06:37.360 --> 06:38.070
I'll go make some food.

06:38.070 --> 06:39.040
It won't take long.

06:39.220 --> 06:39.830
Okay.

06:43.790 --> 06:51.190
♫Sparrows gather on the windowsill, sunlight streaming through♫

06:44.070 --> 06:44.720
I'll be right back.

06:51.500 --> 06:59.240
♫Poets keep altering words to record the fast-changing world♫

06:59.430 --> 07:06.630
♫A relationship or an accident♫

07:07.130 --> 07:10.720
♫It became brighter because of you♫

07:10.840 --> 07:14.790
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

07:14.810 --> 07:18.530
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

07:18.550 --> 07:22.290
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

07:22.480 --> 07:26.290
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

07:26.310 --> 07:30.210
♫I've decided to only love you♫

07:30.040 --> 07:32.360
TCM specialty therapies...

07:30.230 --> 07:32.230
♫My foolishness♫

07:32.250 --> 07:34.100
♫My sincerity♫

07:32.360 --> 07:34.190
The quality of life...

07:34.120 --> 07:36.120
♫Only for one person♫

07:38.950 --> 07:44.490
♫Because of you, everything brightens up♫

07:57.210 --> 08:04.440
♫Waking up from my dream, I'm lost in my emotions♫

08:04.610 --> 08:11.330
♫Continuous gloom, my failures, hard to let go♫

08:12.240 --> 08:20.170
♫But love comes with hurt; I'm a fool, never able to figure it out♫

08:20.280 --> 08:27.560
♫Even if you don't give me an answer about the future♫

08:23.430 --> 08:24.870
Why are you here?

08:25.350 --> 08:27.430
I just came to see if there's anything I can help with.

08:28.140 --> 08:28.990
Can you cook?

08:28.210 --> 08:31.810
♫It became brighter because of you♫

08:29.990 --> 08:30.640
Nope.

08:31.430 --> 08:32.740
Then just watch me cook.

08:31.920 --> 08:35.870
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

08:33.140 --> 08:33.809
Sit for a while.

08:33.840 --> 08:34.490
It'll be ready soon.

08:34.600 --> 08:35.080
Okay.

08:35.900 --> 08:39.610
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

08:39.640 --> 08:43.710
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

08:43.770 --> 08:47.580
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

08:47.610 --> 08:51.500
♫I've decided to only love you♫

08:51.530 --> 08:53.530
♫My foolishness♫

08:53.550 --> 08:55.390
♫My sincerity♫

08:55.420 --> 08:58.000
♫Only for one person♫

09:01.010 --> 09:02.100
This medicinal cuisine

09:02.100 --> 09:03.780
is perfect for autumn nourishment.

09:04.000 --> 09:05.080
You can try it.

09:07.700 --> 09:08.370
Here you are.

09:08.890 --> 09:09.730
Be careful, it's hot.

09:10.010 --> 09:10.580
Thanks.

09:15.060 --> 09:17.890
It smells so good. What did you put in it?

09:18.650 --> 09:20.020
It should be the fragrance of angelica.

09:20.050 --> 09:21.680
Angelica can nourish qi and blood.

09:21.700 --> 09:22.620
It's especially good for you.

09:25.060 --> 09:25.650
Dr. He.

09:26.220 --> 09:27.220
Can I take a picture?

09:27.930 --> 09:28.530
Of course.

09:31.250 --> 09:32.410
Sending it to your friends?

09:33.820 --> 09:34.910
Not really.

09:35.910 --> 09:37.430
"Not really"? What do you mean?

09:38.770 --> 09:40.460
Actually, I came here today

09:40.460 --> 09:41.980
to ask you for some help

09:41.980 --> 09:43.060
with a work thing.

09:44.190 --> 09:46.240
A work thing? What is it?

09:47.310 --> 09:49.980
Our hotel is currently planning a TCM-themed

09:50.010 --> 09:51.490
wellness journey.

09:51.490 --> 09:52.460
Medicinal cuisine is part of it,

09:52.460 --> 09:53.930
so we might need to hire a consultant.

09:53.950 --> 09:55.140
You're the person I thought of.

09:55.380 --> 09:57.980
I wonder if you're available and interested.

09:59.130 --> 10:00.700
If it's just for consulting,

10:01.040 --> 10:01.590
okay,

10:01.610 --> 10:02.610
I can give it a try.

10:04.460 --> 10:05.220
However,

10:05.220 --> 10:06.490
for this consulting work,

10:06.490 --> 10:07.700
do I need to go to your hotel?

10:08.660 --> 10:10.450
It would be best if you could come,

10:10.490 --> 10:11.460
but if you can't,

10:11.460 --> 10:12.940
online consultation is also fine.

10:13.570 --> 10:16.380
I'm on duty at the TCM hospital from Monday to Friday

10:16.850 --> 10:19.010
and at the TCM clinic on Saturdays.

10:19.580 --> 10:20.890
So I'm only free on Sundays.

10:20.970 --> 10:21.730
Would that work for you?

10:21.750 --> 10:23.570
No problem, we can work around your schedule.

10:23.810 --> 10:25.400
Alright, then I'll give it a try.

10:25.530 --> 10:26.060
Great.

10:27.240 --> 10:28.190
As you know,

10:28.420 --> 10:30.650
I have a full-time job at the TCM hospital.

10:31.170 --> 10:32.080
So,

10:32.130 --> 10:34.580
I need to be cautious about external consulting projects.

10:35.250 --> 10:36.160
Can you show me

10:36.190 --> 10:37.400
your specific plan?

10:37.790 --> 10:38.600
No problem.

10:38.890 --> 10:40.060
I'll send it to you once I wrap up

10:40.060 --> 10:41.180
the proposal drafting.

10:41.200 --> 10:43.280
Rest assured, we are absolutely legitimate.

10:43.420 --> 10:44.900
I didn't say you weren't legitimate.

10:45.020 --> 10:46.470
I'm just being cautious.

10:47.400 --> 10:49.790
However, I have a small suggestion.

10:51.820 --> 10:54.530
We don't recommend using the term 'TCM specialty.'

10:55.790 --> 10:57.670
We really don't suggest restaurants

10:57.690 --> 10:59.940
advertise medicinal effects and treatments.

11:00.530 --> 11:01.530
It might cause some

11:01.530 --> 11:03.180
unnecessary troubles and issues.

11:04.980 --> 11:07.420
But going with Chinese herbal wellness is fine.

11:07.440 --> 11:08.750
Focus on gentle health care.

11:09.890 --> 11:10.650
I got it.

11:11.530 --> 11:14.300
Then, Dr. He, let's have a great time working together.

11:15.820 --> 11:16.890
Glad to work with you.

11:22.850 --> 11:23.370
How is it?

11:23.370 --> 11:24.530
It tastes so delicious.

11:24.530 --> 11:25.220
Then have some more.

11:35.490 --> 11:36.770
When I make fish soup,

11:36.770 --> 11:38.000
you can always come over and try it.

11:38.030 --> 11:40.080
I'll serve you clear soup and tender fish.

11:40.740 --> 11:42.500
Okay, thank you for inviting me.

11:43.460 --> 11:44.980
You're usually swamped with work,

11:44.980 --> 11:46.490
yet you still learn to cook for yourself?

11:47.300 --> 11:48.980
I do cook for myself when I'm free.

11:49.100 --> 11:51.450
But I also eat at the hospital cafeteria.

11:51.940 --> 11:54.060
Did you start cooking

11:54.060 --> 11:55.250
to improve your diet?

11:55.300 --> 11:56.220
Nope.

11:56.250 --> 11:57.970
The food at our hospital cafeteria is quite good.

11:58.330 --> 12:00.610
And some dishes also have medicinal herbs added.

12:00.980 --> 12:01.930
Quite unique.

12:02.530 --> 12:04.770
Is it unique in flavor

12:04.770 --> 12:06.820
or just unusual?

12:07.840 --> 12:09.270
I'd say it's a unique flavor.

12:10.430 --> 12:11.790
I thought your hospital cafeteria

12:11.810 --> 12:13.570
was like my college cafeteria,

12:13.610 --> 12:15.060
both unique and unusual.

12:19.890 --> 12:21.130
Let's go, I'll walk you home.

12:21.340 --> 12:22.940
Don't bother. It's not that late.

12:22.940 --> 12:24.530
You can go back and rest.

12:25.790 --> 12:26.360
Okay.

12:26.610 --> 12:27.420
Well, bye-bye.

12:28.130 --> 12:28.520
Good night.

12:32.450 --> 12:33.730
Oh, right, Dr. He,

12:34.100 --> 12:36.300
I was supposed to treat you to dinner today

12:36.300 --> 12:37.610
to invite you to be our consultant.

12:37.610 --> 12:39.770
But you ended up cooking for me instead.

12:40.100 --> 12:41.220
What's the big deal?

12:41.430 --> 12:42.880
The formality isn't that important.

12:42.900 --> 12:45.300
What matters is that we both had a good meal.

12:45.700 --> 12:47.580
No, last time it was moxibustion.

12:47.610 --> 12:49.060
And this time you cooked for me.

12:49.060 --> 12:51.220
Next time, I must treat you to a hearty meal.

12:53.800 --> 12:56.800
Well, if it's your treat, I won't hold back.

12:56.850 --> 12:57.490
Good!

12:57.490 --> 12:58.430
See you next time then.

12:58.450 --> 12:59.330
See you around.

12:59.600 --> 13:00.480
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

13:20.500 --> 13:22.100
Dr. He and I have reached an agreement.

13:22.130 --> 13:23.340
He can be our consultant.

13:23.730 --> 13:25.480
But he still needs our project proposal

13:25.510 --> 13:26.750
for confirmation.

13:31.500 --> 13:32.230
Nice!

13:32.500 --> 13:34.020
Could you give me a copy of his profile?

13:34.040 --> 13:35.240
I'll add it to the slides.

13:36.900 --> 13:38.290
I forgot to ask him for it.

13:38.370 --> 13:39.250
I'll send it to you later.

13:43.890 --> 13:44.820
OK.

13:52.050 --> 13:55.290
The hospital's official website should have this kind of profile, right?

14:11.070 --> 14:13.720
[He Suye]

14:46.540 --> 14:50.380
This ID photo would look a bit out of place on the expert showcase wall.

15:14.770 --> 15:15.470
Are you asleep?

15:19.960 --> 15:21.510
You're fishing for a response again.

15:26.280 --> 15:27.920
Well, looks like you still took the bait.

16:05.340 --> 16:05.890
Hello?

16:06.370 --> 16:06.890
Hello?

16:09.060 --> 16:11.730
Why are you suddenly calling me?

16:16.180 --> 16:17.180
I...

16:17.770 --> 16:18.650
I just wanted to ask you

16:18.650 --> 16:20.890
when the proposal will be completed.

16:21.670 --> 16:23.950
I might need to send two graduate students to help.

16:26.470 --> 16:28.040
Is it okay to finish it within this week?

16:28.730 --> 16:29.490
Yes.

16:30.970 --> 16:33.680
Then you don't need to work overtime tonight.

16:34.950 --> 16:35.740
Okay.

16:37.080 --> 16:38.550
I mean...

16:39.200 --> 16:40.550
You can hit the hay early.

16:44.940 --> 16:46.010
Then I'll

16:46.650 --> 16:47.610
hang up now.

16:48.960 --> 16:49.630
Good night.

16:50.360 --> 16:51.030
Good night.

17:37.410 --> 17:39.060
Didn't expect him to be so professional.

17:39.570 --> 17:41.530
I even thought about changing his prescription before.

17:58.610 --> 17:59.650
Relax, it's okay.

18:00.180 --> 18:01.250
Yes, this acupoint.

18:02.760 --> 18:03.460
Insert the needle.

18:17.990 --> 18:20.470
It's alright, don't be nervous.

18:23.790 --> 18:24.550
It's done.

18:26.530 --> 18:28.220
How do you feel? Still feel like vomiting?

18:29.330 --> 18:30.220
I'm fine now.

18:30.620 --> 18:31.380
No worries.

18:31.620 --> 18:32.900
Vomiting is one of the most common

18:32.900 --> 18:34.220
side effects after chemotherapy.

18:34.770 --> 18:36.140
In terms of TCM,

18:36.140 --> 18:39.330
it's a symptom of stomach disharmony and qi reversal.

18:40.250 --> 18:40.940
As for constipation,

18:40.940 --> 18:42.420
it's a side effect of the antiemetic.

18:43.090 --> 18:44.180
So these two side effects

18:44.180 --> 18:45.380
usually occur simultaneously.

18:47.420 --> 18:48.570
Before the next chemotherapy session,

18:48.570 --> 18:50.730
you can have her drink some Pinellia Soothing Decoction

18:50.730 --> 18:52.140
to avoid these side effects.

18:52.140 --> 18:53.090
Okay, I see.

18:54.330 --> 18:55.290
Come here and learn this.

18:56.080 --> 18:57.800
If the patient still feels nauseous at other times,

18:58.170 --> 18:59.930
you can gently press on the second metacarpal bone

19:00.960 --> 19:02.240
of the right hand.

19:03.790 --> 19:04.980
Feeling a bit sore and swollen, right?

19:06.250 --> 19:07.180
It's normal to feel so.

19:10.140 --> 19:11.810
Press for about a minute,

19:11.810 --> 19:13.010
and it should relieve the symptoms.

19:13.570 --> 19:14.290
Okay, I got it.

19:14.290 --> 19:15.180
Thank you, doctor.

19:17.120 --> 19:17.910
I feel much better now.

19:26.710 --> 19:28.630
Alright, you can get some rest now.

19:28.650 --> 19:30.140
I'll have a doctor come to remove the needle later.

19:30.170 --> 19:31.130
Thank you.

19:35.530 --> 19:37.010
It's not a busy day today.

19:39.230 --> 19:40.230
The food's a bit cold.

19:41.490 --> 19:42.420
Do you want some shrimp?

19:42.910 --> 19:43.600
I'll have one.

19:43.620 --> 19:44.210
Here.

19:46.800 --> 19:47.750
What dish is this?

19:51.920 --> 19:52.960
I think it's a bit too salty.

19:53.330 --> 19:54.120
Li Jie.

19:55.520 --> 19:56.330
This doesn't taste good.

19:56.330 --> 19:56.730
Really?

19:56.810 --> 19:57.650
Li Jie!

20:00.810 --> 20:01.530
This kid,

20:01.530 --> 20:03.220
why is he always clinging to Senior He?

20:04.570 --> 20:05.180
Is that so?

20:05.180 --> 20:05.730
Try one.

20:06.200 --> 20:06.980
I didn't notice it.

20:06.980 --> 20:07.570
I'll have one.

20:16.010 --> 20:16.420
Alright, alright.

20:16.420 --> 20:17.460
Stop playing and eat your meal.

20:23.090 --> 20:23.660
Come on, eat up.

20:23.660 --> 20:24.980
Can I have some of yours?

20:24.980 --> 20:26.980
Your chicken drumstick looks so delicious.

20:27.490 --> 20:29.570
No, you'll have chemotherapy in a couple of days.

20:29.570 --> 20:30.770
You should be careful with your diet.

20:34.460 --> 20:35.770
As I told you before,

20:35.980 --> 20:37.140
the food in this staff cafeteria

20:37.140 --> 20:38.530
isn't even as good as your own meals.

20:38.690 --> 20:39.540
Yet you insisted on coming with me.

20:40.730 --> 20:41.900
My mom has to work.

20:42.050 --> 20:43.460
I don't want her to come all the way here

20:43.460 --> 20:44.250
just to bring me food.

20:45.190 --> 20:46.560
So I'll just make do with this.

20:47.860 --> 20:49.140
Make do with this?

20:50.180 --> 20:51.810
I told you to stay in the ward.

20:51.810 --> 20:52.940
Why do you have to follow me every day?

20:53.750 --> 20:55.360
It's not that I like following you.

20:55.920 --> 20:58.030
You're the only one I'm familiar with in this hospital.

20:58.050 --> 20:58.770
That's right.

20:59.620 --> 21:00.420
After all,

21:01.190 --> 21:02.320
besides my mom,

21:02.350 --> 21:04.110
you're the only one who's seen my butt.

21:06.600 --> 21:07.410
Well,

21:07.980 --> 21:09.220
all those nurses and doctors who helped

21:09.220 --> 21:10.860
deliver you all saw your butt, didn't they?

21:11.270 --> 21:11.700
And also,

21:11.700 --> 21:13.330
hasn't your dad seen your butt too?

21:13.590 --> 21:14.700
I don't have a father.

21:14.720 --> 21:16.610
He died when I was in kindergarten.

21:28.190 --> 21:29.560
I think you're quite like my dad.

21:30.170 --> 21:31.260
That's why I'm following you.

21:40.140 --> 21:41.650
You sweet-talker.

21:44.790 --> 21:46.350
Alright, eat some more at lunch.

21:46.800 --> 21:48.220
Later this afternoon, be a good boy

21:48.250 --> 21:49.790
and stay in the ward to do your homework.

21:49.950 --> 21:51.600
Don't run around, you hear me?

21:53.620 --> 21:55.420
Can I ask you about the questions I can't solve?

21:56.530 --> 21:58.250
Sure, I'm open for appointments this afternoon.

21:58.250 --> 21:59.050
You can make an appointment.

22:00.560 --> 22:01.950
The appointment fee is twenty yuan.

22:03.070 --> 22:06.120
Spending twenty yuan to have you help me with my homework

22:06.250 --> 22:07.140
is not worthwhile!

22:08.670 --> 22:11.250
So you know it's expensive. Then don't run around

22:11.250 --> 22:12.700
and do your homework by yourself.

22:16.490 --> 22:17.490
Eat more vegetables.

22:17.490 --> 22:18.490
Don't just eat rice.

22:19.730 --> 22:20.730
Let's eat them together.

22:21.210 --> 22:22.820
Vegetables are nutritious.

22:24.710 --> 22:26.280
If it's not enough, I'll help you get some more.

22:31.630 --> 22:32.430
What's wrong?

22:33.910 --> 22:34.320
No,

22:34.340 --> 22:35.380
nothing.

22:38.050 --> 22:40.080
This afternoon, Qiu Tian and I will go back to school.

22:40.110 --> 22:42.030
We need to modify the NSFC bidding document

22:42.550 --> 22:45.510
and organize the new breast cancer cases.

22:45.530 --> 22:46.920
Are you two joining the doctor's consultations this afternoon?

22:47.640 --> 22:49.400
You're already at the revision stage?

22:49.840 --> 22:51.390
When on earth will you finish drafting?

22:51.840 --> 22:52.840
Soon, soon.

22:53.690 --> 22:54.780
You'd better hurry up.

22:54.800 --> 22:56.070
It needs to be submitted the day after tomorrow.

22:56.420 --> 22:57.380
I know!

22:57.380 --> 22:58.290
I'll write it right away.

23:04.420 --> 23:05.180
The person in charge of the tour group

23:05.180 --> 23:07.700
has reviewed the TCM wellness tour proposal.

23:07.700 --> 23:08.730
They also find it feasible.

23:08.730 --> 23:09.770
We can proceed with it.

23:10.250 --> 23:11.290
There might be a few tweaks

23:11.290 --> 23:12.980
but no major changes.

23:13.140 --> 23:15.140
Manager Lin will be responsible for communication and follow-up.

23:15.620 --> 23:18.250
Manager Shen will handle housekeeping and reception.

23:19.380 --> 23:20.900
Manager Xu will be in charge of food and beverage.

23:21.140 --> 23:22.250
It's time to contact the suppliers

23:22.250 --> 23:23.480
for ingredients and medicinal herbs.

23:24.330 --> 23:25.060
One more thing.

23:25.330 --> 23:26.010
Manager Shen.

23:26.400 --> 23:28.510
You need to get Dr. He to sign the consultant contract.

23:29.030 --> 23:29.800
Don't worry,

23:29.860 --> 23:31.750
I've already sent him the standard contract.

23:32.050 --> 23:33.730
He's also good with the consulting fee.

23:33.730 --> 23:36.330
There are just some specific details to be adjusted.

23:36.330 --> 23:37.780
I'll hit up the legal team later.

23:37.800 --> 23:40.160
We'll try to get him to sign the contract this week.

23:40.190 --> 23:41.330
So he can start working with us this Sunday.

23:41.360 --> 23:41.940
Alright.

23:41.980 --> 23:43.770
Since you're more familiar with Dr. He,

23:43.770 --> 23:45.140
the following contract signing

23:45.140 --> 23:45.770
will be left to you.

23:46.330 --> 23:46.730
Okay.

23:46.940 --> 23:50.140
Then you guys communicate internally about this.

23:50.320 --> 23:52.510
I'm going to have lunch now.

24:11.260 --> 24:12.500
Is this TCM Physician He

24:13.510 --> 24:15.120
single and open to pursuers?

24:20.810 --> 24:21.700
He's single.

24:22.330 --> 24:22.810
But...

24:22.810 --> 24:24.380
Then introduce him to me.

24:24.480 --> 24:26.130
Let's keep the best within ourselves!

24:32.810 --> 24:35.810
If it's not okay to pursue Dr. He,

24:36.010 --> 24:37.980
what about his relatives,

24:38.900 --> 24:39.830
friends,

24:40.490 --> 24:41.250
or colleagues?

24:41.730 --> 24:42.290
I'm good with any of them.

24:42.570 --> 24:44.290
Could you introduce someone to me?

24:44.660 --> 24:46.530
I didn't say anything.

24:47.770 --> 24:49.490
Manager Shen, I think your luck in love

24:49.490 --> 24:51.140
is so good.

24:52.420 --> 24:54.700
Look at this Dr. He's outstanding appearance.

24:54.960 --> 24:57.400
Oh, and her ex-boyfriend is handsome and rich!

24:58.380 --> 25:00.730
Don't you know her ex-boyfriend is dead?

25:04.980 --> 25:05.730
Um,

25:06.230 --> 25:08.950
If there are no other questions, let's wrap it up here.

25:09.720 --> 25:11.610
Keep in touch for any new updates.

25:11.670 --> 25:12.260
Alright.

25:26.380 --> 25:28.220
Hey, are you available?

25:28.220 --> 25:30.420
I'd like to talk to you about the herb suppliers.

25:31.620 --> 25:32.450
Is that necessary?

25:32.450 --> 25:34.920
We can just ask that TCM consultant when he joins us.

25:44.030 --> 25:45.160
Has Zhang Huming arrived?

25:51.630 --> 25:52.520
Little one.

26:02.620 --> 26:04.570
Your pulse is much steadier this time compared to the last.

26:05.730 --> 26:06.700
Are you still coughing up phlegm?

26:07.530 --> 26:08.330
Not anymore.

26:09.060 --> 26:10.500
I'm not short of breath at night either.

26:10.980 --> 26:11.810
Good.

26:12.250 --> 26:13.490
No other discomforts?

26:14.460 --> 26:15.770
I feel lighter overall,

26:15.770 --> 26:17.250
but sometimes when I'm working,

26:18.250 --> 26:19.010
I get a tight chest

26:19.530 --> 26:20.530
and still a bit out of breath.

26:21.730 --> 26:22.490
That's normal.

26:22.860 --> 26:24.010
After lung cancer surgery,

26:24.010 --> 26:26.140
the lung function will be somewhat affected.

26:28.010 --> 26:29.180
Make sure to work out regularly

26:29.180 --> 26:30.140
and don't overexert yourself.

26:30.420 --> 26:31.010
You'll recover slowly

26:31.010 --> 26:31.860
from this illness.

26:32.380 --> 26:33.490
The medicine I prescribed for you last month,

26:33.490 --> 26:34.530
keep taking it for another month.

26:34.920 --> 26:37.080
Have your local hospital copy the prescription for you.

26:37.140 --> 26:38.180
It'll be cheaper this way.

26:38.900 --> 26:39.900
That's great!

26:39.900 --> 26:40.810
Thank you, Dr. He.

26:40.810 --> 26:41.420
No problem.

26:41.860 --> 26:42.700
Dr. He,

26:43.880 --> 26:45.030
is this your child?

26:47.420 --> 26:48.180
Um...

26:48.530 --> 26:49.820
He's just one of my young patients.

26:49.850 --> 26:51.870
His parent is busy, so she let him come to have fun here.

26:53.040 --> 26:53.910
I thought...

26:54.620 --> 26:57.210
Dr. He, just one word to summarize your character—

26:57.230 --> 26:57.710
trustworthy!

26:58.380 --> 26:59.530
Well, I'll leave then.

26:59.530 --> 27:00.050
Okay...

27:00.050 --> 27:00.620
Goodbye.

27:00.620 --> 27:01.660
Stay in a good mood!

27:01.660 --> 27:03.380
Okay... Thank you!

27:09.280 --> 27:10.040
Zhao Ze.

27:13.130 --> 27:14.960
You're about to have the next chemotherapy session.

27:14.990 --> 27:16.120
Take good care of yourself

27:16.180 --> 27:17.140
and don't run around.

27:17.320 --> 27:18.430
I'm bored.

27:18.810 --> 27:19.490
Bored?

27:19.900 --> 27:21.050
Then go back to do your homework.

27:21.600 --> 27:23.510
Don't end up at the bottom of your grade when you return to school.

27:23.570 --> 27:24.380
It'll be a shame.

27:25.850 --> 27:27.110
Alright, go back now.

27:27.160 --> 27:27.920
Don't wander around.

27:37.860 --> 27:39.220
Don't run around like that again next time.

27:42.690 --> 27:43.650
Sorry.

28:16.380 --> 28:17.250
You came for me?

28:19.660 --> 28:20.810
I'd like to have a chat with you.

28:21.810 --> 28:22.640
About what?

28:25.120 --> 28:27.670
You shouldn't always be following Dr. He.

28:28.290 --> 28:30.290
And don't say anything weird.

28:30.970 --> 28:31.900
What did I say?

28:33.890 --> 28:35.890
You said he's like your dad.

28:36.560 --> 28:38.320
He's a young doctor.

28:38.340 --> 28:39.580
And he's single now.

28:39.980 --> 28:42.280
What you said can easily lead to misunderstandings.

28:42.420 --> 28:43.830
It's not good for his reputation

28:43.850 --> 28:45.330
and career.

28:55.050 --> 28:55.980
I said "like"

28:55.980 --> 28:57.050
but not "is."

29:01.320 --> 29:02.630
Anyway, you're just a kid. You don't understand.

29:03.210 --> 29:04.490
You can't say random things like that anymore.

29:06.140 --> 29:07.140
Do you like him?

29:08.950 --> 29:10.840
D-Don't talk nonsense.

29:11.780 --> 29:13.320
He's like a teacher to me.

29:13.780 --> 29:15.130
Then why do you care so much?

29:32.710 --> 29:34.230
Since your situation is urgent,

29:34.250 --> 29:36.170
give me your health insurance card. I'll help you process it.

29:36.250 --> 29:37.460
Thank you, doctor.

29:37.460 --> 29:38.220
It's my duty.

29:38.580 --> 29:39.430
Just a moment.

29:46.030 --> 29:48.420
Li, please help me mark this patient's case as "urgent."

29:48.750 --> 29:50.190
How many times has this happened this month?

29:50.250 --> 29:51.090
Remember to have patients

29:51.090 --> 29:52.570
make online appointments in advance from now on.

29:52.570 --> 29:53.040
Okay.

29:53.330 --> 29:54.530
Thank you for your help, Li.

30:05.280 --> 30:05.810
Nailed it.

30:05.810 --> 30:06.700
Thank you, doctor.

30:06.720 --> 30:07.850
It's part of my job.

30:08.460 --> 30:09.530
Were it not for your help,

30:09.950 --> 30:11.270
I wouldn't know how to do it.

30:12.170 --> 30:13.900
Come meet me right after your checkup.

30:14.090 --> 30:15.680
I'll wait for the results before I clock out.

30:16.670 --> 30:17.930
Thank you, Dr. He.

30:17.980 --> 30:18.730
Thank you.

30:18.730 --> 30:19.220
It's nothing.

30:20.050 --> 30:22.290
TCM usually considers chemotherapy as a medicinal toxin.

30:22.620 --> 30:23.490
The medicinal toxin in the stomach

30:23.490 --> 30:25.460
damages its normal digestive function.

30:25.920 --> 30:28.470
In this case, stomach qi reverses, causing vomiting.

30:29.140 --> 30:31.340
Acupuncture can be used to alleviate this.

30:32.410 --> 30:35.010
Acupoints can include Zhongwan, Gongsun,

30:35.010 --> 30:37.420
Neiguan, Hegu, and Zusanli.

30:38.340 --> 30:40.820
The reducing method can relieve the patient's symptoms.

30:41.830 --> 30:43.630
You should learn to use both TCM and Western theories

30:43.660 --> 30:44.780
to analyze and explain,

30:44.810 --> 30:46.500
and thus solve practical clinical problems.

30:52.220 --> 30:52.810
Are you alright?

30:53.050 --> 30:53.700
I'm fine.

30:54.020 --> 30:55.310
It's always like this after chemotherapy.

30:55.710 --> 30:56.840
I'm used to it. Let's begin.

30:57.220 --> 30:58.050
You'll feel better soon.

30:58.330 --> 30:59.000
We're starting.

31:20.160 --> 31:20.840
Good.

31:23.010 --> 31:24.490
Besides vomiting, are you also having diarrhea?

31:25.090 --> 31:25.940
Just once.

31:26.620 --> 31:27.530
Any blood in the stool?

31:27.700 --> 31:28.490
No.

31:30.140 --> 31:31.490
You even know that?

31:31.800 --> 31:32.800
Quite professional.

31:33.750 --> 31:35.640
How's your appetite? Do you want to eat?

31:36.030 --> 31:38.360
You just mentioned blood in stool,

31:38.660 --> 31:40.220
so I feel like I shouldn't say I want to eat.

31:44.730 --> 31:47.140
Alright, just rest well then.

31:48.050 --> 31:48.900
Get some good rest.

31:48.900 --> 31:49.700
Be good.

31:55.530 --> 31:56.570
I've prescribed some medicine for him.

31:56.570 --> 31:57.900
Send it to him later.

31:58.510 --> 31:59.880
Let me know if you have any problems.

32:03.800 --> 32:04.670
Dr. He.

32:06.490 --> 32:07.660
I prescribed some medicine for him.

32:07.660 --> 32:09.140
It's for detoxifying and nourishing the spleen and kidneys.

32:09.810 --> 32:10.770
It can go with chemotherapy

32:10.770 --> 32:12.570
and help him expel toxins from his body quickly,

32:13.070 --> 32:14.350
while also replenishing qi and blood.

32:14.370 --> 32:15.960
He can recover faster this way.

32:16.570 --> 32:18.200
Okay, thank you, Dr. He.

32:18.440 --> 32:19.220
Don't worry.

32:19.410 --> 32:21.490
His chemotherapy is showing good results.

32:30.540 --> 32:32.330
You two can go for lunch now.

32:32.960 --> 32:35.160
Who's coming with me for consultations this afternoon?

32:38.840 --> 32:39.910
I'll go.

32:42.530 --> 32:42.860
Hello?

32:43.530 --> 32:44.090
Hello?

32:44.110 --> 32:45.670
Dr. He, are you available now?

32:45.810 --> 32:46.770
I have something to tell you.

32:47.290 --> 32:48.220
Yeah, go ahead.

32:48.940 --> 32:49.860
I've sent the clean version

32:49.860 --> 32:51.380
of the contract to your email.

32:51.380 --> 32:52.620
Please check it out.

32:52.860 --> 32:54.530
If everything looks good,

32:54.530 --> 32:56.570
please snap photos of both sides of your ID card

32:56.570 --> 32:57.900
and send them to me.

32:57.970 --> 32:59.210
I need to include them in the contract.

32:59.240 --> 33:00.960
Then I can get it stamped by the legal team.

33:01.650 --> 33:02.850
Alright, I'll check the mail.

33:06.940 --> 33:07.700
Dr. He,

33:08.130 --> 33:09.680
are you busy today?

33:09.710 --> 33:12.320
How about I go to your hospital for your signature?

33:12.810 --> 33:20.240
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

33:14.420 --> 33:15.290
This way,

33:15.290 --> 33:16.050
we can finish signing today,

33:16.050 --> 33:18.090
and I can apply for your consultant fee this afternoon.

33:18.380 --> 33:19.860
You can start working with us this Sunday.

33:20.180 --> 33:21.180
Otherwise,

33:20.920 --> 33:28.610
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

33:21.180 --> 33:22.860
if it gets pushed to next week,

33:23.140 --> 33:25.330
we might be running short of time.

33:26.490 --> 33:28.140
Okay, you can come over anytime.

33:29.160 --> 33:32.570
Is it okay if I go meet you around 11:30?

33:29.180 --> 33:36.430
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

33:33.430 --> 33:34.120
No problem.

33:35.560 --> 33:36.190
See you then.

33:36.740 --> 33:43.680
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

33:36.890 --> 33:37.850
See you later.

33:46.490 --> 33:47.900
I need any one of you to go with me this afternoon.

33:53.400 --> 33:54.160
Kexin,

33:55.250 --> 33:56.290
don't you think

33:56.290 --> 34:00.530
Suye has been in an unusually good mood lately?

34:01.340 --> 34:02.250
Yeah...

34:03.730 --> 34:04.530
It's like

34:05.720 --> 34:07.810
a rare romantic vibe.

34:11.639 --> 34:12.199
Let's go.

34:24.130 --> 34:25.820
He's so chill about it.

34:26.199 --> 34:27.630
He didn't even add a watermark.

34:37.280 --> 34:42.850
[Only for the consultant contract with Gunan Huating Hotel. It's invalid for any other use.]

35:38.890 --> 35:39.930
Hi.

35:39.960 --> 35:40.920
Have you been waiting long?

35:42.300 --> 35:43.490
Not really.

35:43.880 --> 35:45.400
It's just rare for me to skip work.

35:45.430 --> 35:46.460
I'm extraordinarily happy today.

35:46.480 --> 35:48.290
When I'm happy, I tend to get sleepy.

35:48.610 --> 35:49.450
Get sleepy?

35:56.570 --> 35:56.990
Come on,

35:57.010 --> 35:57.650
follow me.

35:59.170 --> 35:59.680
Come on!

36:07.100 --> 36:08.910
Look, this is the five-flavor fruit.

36:09.380 --> 36:10.780
The one I made tea with for you last time.

36:11.870 --> 36:13.340
So it's these red berries.

36:14.050 --> 36:15.050
Is it also a kind of medicine?

36:15.050 --> 36:15.690
That's right.

36:19.900 --> 36:20.740
What are you doing?

36:24.210 --> 36:24.820
Try it.

36:25.170 --> 36:27.690
Dr. He, even children know

36:27.690 --> 36:29.560
we should protect public plants and trees.

36:29.580 --> 36:30.940
Yet you just picked the fruit straight off.

36:30.970 --> 36:32.530
Just one bunch, it's fine.

36:33.200 --> 36:33.760
Try it.

36:35.050 --> 36:36.210
This thing...

36:36.720 --> 36:37.760
Can we eat it directly?

36:37.790 --> 36:38.710
Of course.

36:39.490 --> 36:40.210
Give it a try.

36:56.260 --> 36:57.860
Chew the pit as well.

37:01.940 --> 37:02.610
It tastes awful!

37:02.610 --> 37:03.650
What is that?

37:03.820 --> 37:04.490
The inside

37:04.490 --> 37:05.530
tastes like the Sichuan pepper,

37:05.530 --> 37:07.130
with a hint of bitterness and saltiness.

37:07.380 --> 37:10.050
The sour, sweet, bitter, salty, and spicy are the five flavors of five-flavor fruit.

37:11.590 --> 37:13.470
How is it? Does it wake you up?

37:13.660 --> 37:15.140
What a man...

37:15.170 --> 37:16.380
I saw you getting drowsy!

37:17.300 --> 37:18.740
This works better than coffee.

37:19.020 --> 37:19.910
Thank you.

37:20.090 --> 37:20.490
Have some more.

37:20.490 --> 37:20.980
No...

37:20.980 --> 37:21.780
It tastes terrible.

37:22.190 --> 37:23.270
Come on, have a bit more.

37:24.290 --> 37:25.320
Here you are, the contract.

37:25.650 --> 37:26.740
The hotel has stamped it.

37:26.740 --> 37:27.650
You can sign it now.

37:28.340 --> 37:29.380
You sound like

37:29.710 --> 37:31.920
you're ordering me to sign some kind of slave contract.

37:32.210 --> 37:33.050
Then don't sign it. Give it to me.

37:33.050 --> 37:34.170
I'll sign it...

37:35.530 --> 37:36.530
If I don't sign,

37:36.690 --> 37:37.300
wouldn't you have been

37:37.300 --> 37:38.940
beguiled into eating the five-flavor fruit for nothing?

37:40.550 --> 37:41.530
You're right.

37:45.900 --> 37:46.460
Alright.

37:47.530 --> 37:48.340
It's a pleasure working with you.

37:49.530 --> 37:50.420
Glad to work with you too.

37:54.490 --> 37:55.650
Are you in a hurry to leave?

37:56.850 --> 37:57.650
No.

37:57.910 --> 37:59.760
I just need to file the contract when I get back.

37:59.830 --> 38:01.060
And I've already applied

38:01.090 --> 38:02.420
for the payment request in advance.

38:03.750 --> 38:05.580
How about chilling here with me for a while?

38:07.940 --> 38:08.570
Okay.

38:08.990 --> 38:10.320
Aren't you busy now?

38:10.900 --> 38:11.820
I just finished checking the wards.

38:12.090 --> 38:13.010
The work's set for the afternoon.

38:13.010 --> 38:13.740
I'm free now.

38:15.170 --> 38:15.780
Okay.

38:24.130 --> 38:25.460
I really like it here.

38:25.960 --> 38:28.440
I found it really cozy when I came last time.

38:29.210 --> 38:29.900
Yes,

38:30.340 --> 38:31.460
there are many plants around.

38:31.990 --> 38:32.990
It's especially easy

38:33.340 --> 38:34.180
to get drowsy

38:34.260 --> 38:34.980
and doze off.

38:52.050 --> 38:59.280
♫Waking up from my dream, I'm lost in my emotions♫

38:59.450 --> 39:06.170
♫Continuous gloom, my failures, hard to let go♫

39:07.080 --> 39:15.010
♫But love comes with hurt; I'm a fool, never able to figure it out♫

39:15.120 --> 39:22.410
♫Even if you don't give me an answer about the future♫

39:23.050 --> 39:26.650
♫It became brighter because of you♫

39:26.770 --> 39:30.710
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

39:30.740 --> 39:34.450
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

39:34.480 --> 39:38.550
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

39:38.610 --> 39:42.420
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

39:42.450 --> 39:46.340
♫I've decided to only love you♫

39:46.370 --> 39:48.370
♫My foolishness♫

39:48.390 --> 39:50.230
♫My sincerity♫

39:50.260 --> 39:52.840
♫Only for one person♫

39:54.950 --> 39:59.480
♫Because of you, everything brightens up♫

40:00.870 --> 40:01.630
My call.

40:06.110 --> 40:06.630
Hello?

40:06.650 --> 40:09.170
Senior He, can you come back to the department now?

40:10.210 --> 40:11.050
Something's up, right?

40:11.370 --> 40:13.040
There's an X-ray we're not sure about.

40:13.570 --> 40:14.130
I see.

40:17.170 --> 40:18.300
Well, I have something urgent to handle.

40:18.300 --> 40:19.090
I need to go back.

40:19.490 --> 40:20.820
It's okay. Just go ahead.

40:21.050 --> 40:22.260
I'll also be heading back to the hotel soon.

40:22.690 --> 40:23.900
Okay, see you around.

40:24.570 --> 40:25.050
Bye-bye.

40:25.070 --> 40:25.630
Bye-bye.

40:55.350 --> 40:56.830
[Oncology]

41:41.780 --> 41:42.460
Hello.

41:43.340 --> 41:43.780
Hello.

41:43.780 --> 41:45.380
We don't start consultations until 1:30 p.m. here.

41:46.500 --> 41:47.830
I'm not here for a consultation.

41:47.860 --> 41:49.010
I'm here to meet Dr. He.

41:50.710 --> 41:52.050
For what?

41:53.000 --> 41:54.210
I have something to give him.

41:55.680 --> 41:57.840
He should be in the inpatient department upstairs right now.

41:59.030 --> 42:00.840
Which floor is the inpatient department on?

42:01.070 --> 42:01.680
8th floor.

42:02.010 --> 42:02.780
Okay, thank you.

42:02.950 --> 42:04.500
If you have anything for him, you can give it to me.

42:04.530 --> 42:05.780
I'll help you pass it on to him.

42:06.190 --> 42:07.820
Thanks, but no. It's something quite important.

42:07.820 --> 42:08.890
I'll go send it myself.

42:08.920 --> 42:09.520
Thank you.

42:37.170 --> 42:37.940
-Dr. He...
-Dad!

42:43.120 --> 42:43.920
Dad!

42:45.730 --> 42:46.640
Why are you running so fast?

42:46.720 --> 42:47.610
Where have you been for fun?

42:47.670 --> 42:48.830
The toy store.

42:49.700 --> 42:50.820
